msgctxt "an10.177:13.2"
msgid "Yañca kho so dātā hoti samaṇassa vā brāhmaṇassa vā annaṃ pānaṃ vatthaṃ yānaṃ mālāgandhavilepanaṃ seyyāvasathapadīpeyyaṃ, tena so tattha lābhī hoti annassa pānassa mālānānālaṅkārassa. "
msgstr "Since they gave to ascetics or brahmins … they get to have food and drink, garlands and various adornments. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
