msgctxt "an10.177:14.1"
msgid "Idha pana, brāhmaṇa, ekacco pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti … pe … sammādiṭṭhiko hoti. "
msgstr "Take someone else who doesn’t kill living creatures, steal, or commit sexual misconduct. They don’t use speech that’s false, divisive, harsh, or nonsensical. And they’re contented, kind-hearted, with right view. "

msgctxt "an10.177:14.2"
msgid "So dātā hoti samaṇassa vā brāhmaṇassa vā annaṃ pānaṃ vatthaṃ yānaṃ mālāgandhavilepanaṃ seyyāvasathapadīpeyyaṃ. "
msgstr "They give to ascetics or brahmins … "

msgctxt "an10.177:14.3"
msgid "So kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā manussānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "When their body breaks up, after death, they’re reborn in the human realm. "

msgctxt "an10.177:14.4"
msgid "So tattha lābhī hoti mānusakānaṃ pañcannaṃ kāmaguṇānaṃ. "
msgstr "There they get to have the five kinds of human sensual stimulation. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc15
msgctxt "an10.177:15.1"
msgid "Yaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, idha pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti … pe … sammādiṭṭhiko, tena so kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā manussānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "Since in this life they didn’t kill living creatures … and had right view, they were reborn in the company of humans. "

msgctxt "an10.177:15.2"
msgid "Yañca kho so dātā hoti samaṇassa vā brāhmaṇassa vā annaṃ pānaṃ vatthaṃ yānaṃ mālāgandhavilepanaṃ seyyāvasathapadīpeyyaṃ, tena so tattha lābhī hoti mānusakānaṃ pañcannaṃ kāmaguṇānaṃ. "
