#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.273, sc16
msgctxt "an10.177:16.1"
msgid "Idha pana, brāhmaṇa, ekacco pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti … pe … sammādiṭṭhiko hoti. "
msgstr "Take someone else who doesn’t kill living creatures … and has right view. "

