#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc17
msgctxt "an10.177:17.1"
msgid "Yaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, idha pāṇātipātā paṭivirato hoti … pe … sammādiṭṭhiko, tena so kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā devānaṃ sahabyataṃ upapajjati. "
msgstr "Since in this life they didn’t kill living creatures … and had right view, they were reborn in the company of the gods. "

