msgid "Yañca kho so dātā hoti samaṇassa vā brāhmaṇassa vā annaṃ pānaṃ vatthaṃ yānaṃ mālāgandhavilepanaṃ seyyāvasathapadīpeyyaṃ, tena so tattha lābhī hoti dibbānaṃ pañcannaṃ kāmaguṇānaṃ. "
msgstr "Since they gave to ascetics or brahmins … they get to have the five kinds of heavenly sensual stimulation. "

msgctxt "an10.177:17.3"
msgid "Api ca, brāhmaṇa, dāyakopi anipphalo”ti. "
msgstr "It’s never fruitless for the donor.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc18
msgctxt "an10.177:18.1"
msgid "“Acchariyaṃ, bho gotama, abbhutaṃ, bho gotama. "
msgstr "“It’s incredible, Master Gotama, it’s amazing, "

msgctxt "an10.177:18.2"
msgid "Yāvañcidaṃ, bho gotama, alameva dānāni dātuṃ, alaṃ saddhāni kātuṃ, yatra hi nāma dāyakopi anipphalo”ti. "
msgstr "Just this much is quite enough to justify giving gifts and performing memorial rites for the dead, since it’s never fruitless for the donor.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. VAR: Evametaṃ, brāhmaṇa → evametaṃ brāhmaṇa evametaṃ brāhmaṇa (bj, s1-3)
msgctxt "an10.177:18.3"
msgid "“Evametaṃ, brāhmaṇa, dāyakopi hi, brāhmaṇa, anipphalo”ti. "
msgstr "“That’s so true, brahmin. It’s never fruitless for the donor.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc19
msgctxt "an10.177:19.1"
msgid "“Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! … "

msgctxt "an10.177:19.2"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.177:19.3"
msgid "Ekādasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.177:19.4"
msgid "Jāṇussoṇivaggo dutiyo. "
msgstr ""

